Doors open: 19:00

Frank Carter & The Rattlesnakes
One of the most exciting British live bands are back. Frank Carter & The Rattlesnakes today announce that they are hitting the road in the UK again with a run of dates that kick off in Manchester on 2nd November and include a show at London’s Electric Ballroom.

The news comes ahead of a slew of festivals the band are set to play this month, including the main stage at Reading and Leeds. Preceding the UK tour, Frank Carter & The Rattlesnakes, are on tour in Europe and playing soon to be sold out shows in France, Holland, Denmark and Italy to name a few.
